message.body: How do you feel about working from 6-8 and then an hour movie? I think daylight savings may mess with me on the later end.
Also let me know if tonight still works :)
Hey! I was just going to text you. I think I'm gonna bail tonight. I'm still on the bus and feeling exhausted!
I was going to rally but i bit off more than I could chew this weekend
Totally fine - I am tired too!
Let's be in touch tomorrow about another time
You go away this upcoming weekend ?
Sounds good. I'll be in there Tuesday but not sure what time yet.
Yay! So exciting - I was going to paint ceramics at home on Tuesday but maybe I will join you in the studio- let me know what time you are heading there - but no pressure!
Yeah I'll try to go in the afternoon/evening and maybe we can overlap some!
